That suggests a Pantheon principle.

Symbolic Triangulation

A symbol gains precision not by adding words but by increasing independent dimensions of relation.

Suppose the symbol is

Mirror

It might simultaneously occupy coordinates in

* optics
* symmetry
* self-reference
* information
* inversion
* computation
* psychology

Every new independent axis reduces ambiguity.

The symbol hasn’t become longer.

It has become deeper.

